==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A cylindrical wooden, metal etc. object used to fasten or as a bearing between objects.
# A [[protrusion]] used to hang things on.
# {{cattag|Cribbage}}: A peg moved on a crib board to keep score.

